<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddd3b2ee2-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06" identifier="/us/usc/t12/s4710"><num value="4710">§ 4710.</num><heading> Collection and compilation of information</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Fund shall—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="iddd3b2ee3-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06" identifier="/us/usc/t12/s4710/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> collect and compile information pertinent to community development financial institutions that will assist in creating, developing, expanding, and preserving such institutions; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="iddd3b2ee4-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06" identifier="/us/usc/t12/s4710/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> make such information available to promote the purposes of this subchapter.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="iddd3b2ee5-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/325/tI/s111">Pub. L. 103–325, title I, § 111</ref>, <date date="1994-09-23">Sept. 23, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/2177">108 Stat. 2177</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
